data.description: Call for Lender Incentives on this Property! Welcome to this stunning and meticulously updated home that offers an array of modern amenities and luxurious features. Nestled in the much sought-after Parkstone neighborhood, this 5-bedroom, 3-full bathroom gem is the epitome of comfortable and elegant living. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the exquisite details and top-notch craftsmanship that have gone into every corner of this home. The chef-like kitchen, with its open views, is a culinary enthusiast's dream, boasting loads of storage and ample counter space ideal for both daily living and entertaining guests. Open views to the stately family room adorned with cozy gas fireplace creates a warm and inviting atmosphere for gatherings with friends and family. The separate Dining Room offers the perfect space for holiday gatherings as well as small intimate dinners. At the end of the day escape to the oversized Master with huge walkin and your very own spa like Master bath. This stunning Bath has undergone a full renovation with NEW features, including tile showers, tile floors, toilets, and vanities. The stand alone tub and massive tile shower offer you an amazing oasis, allowing you to unwind and rejuvenate in style. This home is complemented by brand NEW LVP flooring throughout and NEW premier plush carpeting in the Bedrooms enhancing the overall aesthetic. You'll appreciate the thoughtful updates throughout the home, including NEW fans and light fixtures, as well as fresh interior paint. NEW exterior paint adds to the home's curb appeal, and the freshly landscaped yard, along with a recent pressure wash, ensures that the exterior shines as much as the interior. NEW HVAC and water heater. This property offers the convenience of a 2-car garage and a full unfinished basement  that is plumbed, offering endless possibilities for customization and expansion. Outside, the flat backyard backs up to serene woods, providing privacy and a peaceful backdrop. And that's not all—this fantastic neighborhood boasts a range of amazing amenities, including tennis courts, a sparkling pool, a playground, and more. It's a true community where you can enjoy an active and vibrant lifestyle.In summary, this remarkable home is a perfect blend of modern luxury and functionality. With its impeccable updates, stunning features, and sought-after location, it offers an exceptional opportunity for anyone looking to elevate their lifestyle. Don't miss the chance to make this your dream!
